title: Rainbow Gallery Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Beer/Wine, Asian, Fusion, Australian, Malaysian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Cafe in the Pyrenees wine region with overnight cottages onsite. Offers a separate vegan menu Mon-Sat. On Sunday meals are entirely vegan with an all day breakfast and light lunch. Vegan food is prepared in a separate kitchen by vegan chef.
